Summarize Complex Data with Matrix Reports

Get a comprehensive view of your data at a glance by grouping Data Cloud records in a matrix format. Surface trends across sections of the data by comparing subtotals. For a broader perspective, review the totals and grand totals in the report.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

How: From the Reports tab or from the report run page, click next to a field name and select Groups Rows by This Field or Groups Columns by This Field.
title: Matrix Reporting in Salesforce
